Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE & NSL Property Group are pleased to present 16-20 King Street for sale.

This well-presented 930sqm* office/warehouse (plus yard space) across two titles is nestled in the tightly held commercial pocket of Airport West. It offers a rare opportunity to relocate your business close to Essendon Fields and allows for future expansion, development (STCA), or take advantage of the leaseback opportunity to a well-established business.

Situated just off Matthews Avenue, this property has direct access onto the Tullamarine Freeway, Essendon Fields, and is located 7km from Melbourne Airport and 12km from the CBD.

Property Features Include:
+ Total land area: 2,274 sqm*
+ Total building area: 930sqm*
+ Office area: 124sqm*
+ Warehouse area: 806sqm*
+ Extra yard (own title): 738sqm*
+ Vacant possession or leaseback opportunity available
+ Zoned Commercial 2 providing great flexibility
+ Separately titled
+ Two (2) container height roller doors
+ Dual crossing
+ Three (3) phase power
+ Ample amenities including shower
+ Fourteen (14) on-site car spaces

For further details on this property or your Airport West commercial property needs, please contact the marketing agents Jake George on 0421 221 019 or Guy Naselli on 0413 750 744

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusively appointed agents, is pleased to  offer 22-28 Hawker Street, Airport West, for sale via Expressions of Interest closing Wednesday 9th October 2019 at 3pm.

The site is strategically located in the heart of Airport West, capturing the gentrified growth of Melbourne’s north-western corridor. 

22-28 Hawker Street is well connected to all major transport forms, and has direct access to the Melbourne CBD via the Tullamarine Freeway, only 100m* away. Shopping and retail amenity are in abundance, with Airport West Westfield Shopping Centre (300m*) only a short walk away.

Key property attributes include:
+ Total site area: 6,131sqm*
+ Total building area: 2,717sqm*
+ Eight (8) titles
+ Two (2) street frontages (four titles on each)
+ Current net income of $215,000 pa with future increases
+ Securely leased until October 2021
+ Commercial 2 Zone (B3Z)
+ Unique opportunity to invest and re-lease, occupy in the future or re-develop to a higher and better use (STCA).

For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection of the site, kindly contact CBRE.
